OL,3,CWirral man rowing across the Atlantic
OL,4,Cfound dead in his boat
OL,6,FA man has died while attempting to row
OL,7,Fthe Atlantic Ocean in a charity
OL,8,Fchallenge.
OL,10,FMichael Holt, 54, from Heswall,
OL,11,FWirral, had set off in January to row
OL,12,Fsolo from Gran Canaria to Barbados,
OL,13,F3,100 miles across the Atlantic.
OL,15,FBut, after supporters raised concerns
OL,16,Fthey had lost communication with
OL,17,FMichael, formerly of Porthmadog, and
OL,18,Fhis body was found in the cabin of his
OL,19,Fboat by rescuers.
