OL,6,FBut, his Facebook page, a post on 20
OL,7,FFebruary, said Michael had fallen ill
OL,8,Fdue to a reaction to the antibiotics
OL,9,Fhe had taken, and had decided to
OL,10,Fabandon his row, instead heading for
OL,11,FCape Verde.
OL,13,FHis family then lost touch with him,
OL,14,Fand a MayDay signal was sent out,
OL,15,Fwhich alerted a fishing vessel and
OL,16,Ftanker.
OL,18,FA post on the same page in February
OL,19,Fdescribed Michael as someone who saw
OL,20,F'the big picture' and understood the
OL,21,F'enormity' of what he was taking on.
