OL,6,FIt said: "He certainly isn't worried
OL,7,Fabout world record speeds or getting
OL,8,Fanywhere by a specific time - he will
OL,9,Fmake the best progress he can in the
OL,10,Fconditions that he is presented...but
OL,11,Fthis is about the journey, and what he
OL,12,Flearns along the way."
OL,14,FMichael was , which works to support
OL,15,FLiverpool's voluntary communities.
OL,17,FHe was a diabetic and said witnessing
OL,18,F"the challenges of dealing with,
OL,19,Fmanaging and living with Type 1
OL,20,FDiabetes on a daily basis" had
OL,21,Fprompted him to take on the challenge.
